\n[\"hubot-github-pr-assign-notification\"]\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n\n   HUBOT_GITHUB_USERNAME_ROOM_MAPPINGS - A mapping of which github username and chat room belong together.\n   (example:\n   HUBOT_GITHUB_USERNAME_ROOM_MAPPINGS = user1:room1, user2:room2...\n   So when user1 is assigned a PR the bot posts to room1.)\n\n   In addition, you will have to do the following:\n   1. Create a new webhook for your `myuser/myrepo` repository at:\n    https://github.com/myuser/myrepo/settings/hooks/new\n\n   2. Select the individual events to minimize the load on your Hubot.\n\n   3. Add the url: <HUBOT_URL>:<PORT>/hubot/gh-repo-events\n","maintainers":[{"name":"ram535ii","email":"constantijnschepens@gmail.com"}],"time":{"modified":"2015-10-15T19:55:59.237Z","created":"2015-10-15T19:55:59.237Z","0.0.1":"2015-10-15T19:55:59.237Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/ram535ii/hubot-github-pr-assign-notification","keywords":["hubot","hubot-scripts","github"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/ram535ii/hubot-github-pr-assign-notification.git"},"author":{"name":"Constantijn Schepens","email":"constantijnschepens@gmail.com"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/ram535ii/hubot-github-pr-assign-notification/issues"},"license":"MIT","readmeFilename":"README.md"}
